-- MOVES-ALFI names Marc-Andre Bechet director of legal and tax
-- 
-- Fri Sep 12, 2014 07:32AM EDT
-- None



Sept 12 (Reuters) - The Association of the Luxembourg Fund Industry (ALFI) said it appointed Marc-Andre Bechet director of legal and tax, effective Sept. 15.

Bechet was previously head of investment funds services at Banque Degroof Luxembourg, responsible for fund administration and custody. He was also a member of the company's management board.